Title: Marceline's Closet
Writer: Jesse Moynihan, Mark Banker (story), Kent Osborne (story), Pendleton Ward (story), Patrick McHale (story)
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Olivia Olson
Plot: Bored waiting for her, Finn and Jake sneak into Marceline's house, become trapped when she comes home, and witness her strange behavior when she's alone.
